# LiveOps_Design

## 1. Applies when
Mobile / live-service games with seasons, events, operational content, or long-term
updates.

## 2. This document owns
Season structure; event calendar; battle pass; limited-time modes; rerun rules;
operational cadence; version cadence.

## 3. This document does NOT own
Core gameplay numbers; monetization pricing (Monetization_Design); economy base
(Resource_And_Economy).

## 4. Recommended chapter structure
1. Document role · 2. Season structure · 3. Event calendar · 4. Battle pass ·
5. Limited-time content · 6. Rerun rules · 7. Cadence · 8. TODO

## 5. Common boundaries
- LiveOps vs Event Design — cadence/structure vs individual event content.
- LiveOps vs Monetization — operational content vs paid points.
- Progression vs Economy — season progression vs currency.

## 6. Common audit rules
- Event cycle has a single authority.
- Reward tables not duplicated; version content status tracked.
